此，即使我遲到了，我也要祝賀蔡英文總統就職。」<br />\n<br />\n根據曝光的信函圖片，該信在台灣總統就職典禮前一週寄發給巴西眾議院。中國大使館在信中重申「一中原則」是國際社會的共識，也是政府間維繫關係的政治基礎。<br />\n<br />\n中國大使館指出，台灣議題是中國內政、更直接牽涉中國核心國家利益，今年5月20日是「中國台灣地區領導人蔡英文」的就職活動，基於雙方關係，中國採取此提前與必要的方式告知議員們此議題的敏感性，避免議員做出單方面損及中國利益的舉動，包括發送祝賀消息或與台灣保持聯繫，中國對此高度重視。<br />\n<br />\n外交部也回覆馬丁斯該則推文，代表我國政府與人民感謝他的祝賀；馬丁斯則再次回覆說，捍衛自由是他的榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3177343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3177343&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=8e02bb48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3177343&h=fb0edeef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3177343</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"十幾日前嘅信<br />\n而家先放料出黎<br />\n<br />\n合理推斷，其實巴西都係響應美國夾攻支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6efc30df06104592e5d03b9bb31166516b5ec3","tid":2035794,"uid":229395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28381e7ebb5bcc44b407463b27b1aed2d009e77e","tid":2035794,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b4180629440a89c34b629bd0a52d62525418b7","tid":2035794,"uid":184131,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"7 到唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"相比法國領事館嗰單，呢單小巫見大巫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"Info?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f780c0e350944f537624438f301b3e5e5788795","tid":2035794,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60bd730078ed6984e1ac602f50015b4c862ebec4","tid":2035794,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"#VivaTaiwan"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:27